description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a motivated receptionist/administrator to join our administration team at Crewkerne Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have previous reception experience; possess excellent customer service, administrative and IT skills. We require a conscientious candidate who can work under pressure and is eager to learn. You must also be able to communicate with colleagues, the general public and representatives from other organisations, with the ability to provide a friendly and efficient front desk service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An outgoing personality and a professional approach is essential as you will be the initial point of contact for our patients and visitors as well as assisting medical and other hospital staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexibility to cover sickness and holidays is essential. You must also have flexibility to cover absences at other sites within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Uniform will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gillian Wallace Senior Administrator, Chard &amp; Crewkerne Hospitals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;gill.wallace@somersetft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01460 72491&lt;/p&gt;
